{"tid":56127,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SMAP最後合體！90度鞠躬謝幕3分鐘 中居正廣轉身掩面痛哭","createTime":"2016-12-27T03:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T04:03:22.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b67c69ea13d5cb5b3f314f4a46ebee1bc3b6f752","tid":56127,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1544/1544300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1544%2F1544300.jpg&h=9017a029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SMAP主持20年的節目播出最後一集，隊長中居正廣忍不住爆哭，令粉絲跟著淚崩。<br />\n<br />\n日本國民天團SMAP確定解散，合體主持20年的《SMAPXSMAP》於26日正式畫下句點，電視台更以5小時特別節目播出。眾團員在最後的舞台演唱《世界唯一僅有的花》，透過鏡頭向全國粉絲深深90度鞠躬道別，隊長中居正廣更是爆哭，心酸場面令網友跟著心痛！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2236/d2236361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2236%2Fd2236361.jpg&h=0dc71c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SMAP在演唱完《世界唯一僅有的花》後，深深90度鞠躬，感謝粉絲的愛戴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ws1zEzh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fws1zEzh.jpg&h=5033f3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《世界唯一僅有的花》是SMAP的代表金曲，解散消息爆發後，歌迷自動發起購買單曲運動，讓銷量突破300萬張的新高紀錄。5人唱完後站成一排鞠躬謝幕，象徵SMAP正式分道揚鑣，大幕緩緩落下，工作人員也激動鼓掌致意。此時，中居正廣的腰彎得比其他人都低，難掩哀傷表情，接著往舞台後方走去默默哭泣，淚水擦了又流下來，網友見到畫面也難忍痛哭，推特留言「他是最棒的隊長」、「是我從小到大最喜歡的團體」、「我也跟著淚流不止。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2236/d2236360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2236%2Fd2236360.jpg&h=c16d1cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲SMAP隊長中居正廣（中）彎腰比其他人還低，鞠躬時難掩悲傷情緒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2236/d2236358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2236%2Fd2236358.jpg&h=2b053bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中居正廣默默走到舞台後方繼續哭泣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2236/d2236359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2236%2Fd2236359.jpg&h=e7af3b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲中居正廣眼淚擦了又流，這一幕讓觀眾也跟著哭了。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中居正廣在演唱時聲音哽咽，唱到尾聲時舉手揮別，手勢比出「5、4、3、2、1」，有粉絲解讀「5個人的SMAP」，也是逼哭許多觀眾的淚點。此外，電視台在最後一集節目中，解禁前團員森且行的演出身影，當時6人演唱《best friend》，眾人也哭成一團，他也泣不成聲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rja327x4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frja327x4&h=445ffb92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《SMAPXSMAP》播出20年9個月，5人各自在演藝圈都闖出不凡成績，讓節目人氣再往上加分，連外國巨星訪日也必上該節目。此外，草彅剛在節目中的短劇扮演「杯緣子」，喜感演出掀起全亞洲模仿熱潮，天團節目告終，大批民眾直奔到電視台和節目牆拍照留念，也有觀眾傳真到節目留言表達不捨，見證了天團成軍28年來和觀眾間累積的感情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w6DEe8yftOM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw6DEe8yftOM&d=tC8wHLE06i9okBTfUkldoqEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=2cd2a3c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w6DEe8yftOM</a><br />\n▲SMAP主持的節目26日畫下句點，最後的舞台演唱，隊長中居正廣爆哭。"},{"pid":"75083080c6b5c38673a7f649adab1c129cc06d38","tid":56127,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972870fc4f4422be44c3716c62e969d0c009e28a","tid":56127,"uid":68375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54309e77a965a5792fd6678d5cfc3883afc0fd97","tid":56127,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4578d5811d84fc33ea604987d11133824b3448","tid":56127,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"中居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}